Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:04.32,Haiyore-internal/narrator,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Hiro-kun? It's Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:05.10,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.49,0:00:07.99,Haiyore-internal/narrator,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be home in 40 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:09.40,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.81,0:00:11.74,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mahiro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:14.74,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, you are pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:16.61,Haiyore-internal/narrator,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:18.16,Haiyore-internal/narrator,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:20.54,Haiyore-internal/narrator,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. \NOf course it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:22.25,Haiyore-internal/narrator,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:25.25,Haiyore-internal/narrator,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to explain {\i0}them{\i1}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:27.24,Haiyore-internal/narrator,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Would she believe me if I told her
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:29.69,Haiyore-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,they moved in without my permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.00,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry, but I am not \Ninterested in you, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:36.39,Haiyore-internal/narrator,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not careful, she'll \Nthink I'm the kind of son
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:39.39,Haiyore-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,who brings girls home \Nwhile his parents are out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:43.93,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,If you stare at me like that, \Nyou'll make me pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:48.40,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.59,0:00:50.68,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:52.65,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I object to this unjust treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:54.66,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:00:56.16,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here, aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:05.68,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:09.79,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:16.49,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You came back...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:20.34,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mahiro-san, the light's still on.\N You're so forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.34,0:01:24.16,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Boy, you must have some \Nguts to assault Nyarko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:22.79,Haiyore-overlap,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}More, more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:26.24,Haiyore-overlap,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back. Your mother's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:27.94,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:46.71,Haiyore-title-top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,150)}Haiyore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:46.71,Haiyore-title-bottom,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,150)}Nyarko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:09.83,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:12.21,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.79,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.84,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:18.87,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I am the chaos that always
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:23.17,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,crawls up to your son with \Na smile, Nyarlathotep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.85,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nyarlathotep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.55,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,In order to bear Mahiro-san's child,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:29.08,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come from the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:32.03,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, I have come \Nfrom a distant planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:33.38,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Please think of me as your
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:35.36,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,son's wife and call me Nyarko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.36,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't anyone's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.90,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Boy's mother, it is nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.53,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Nyarko's wife, Cthugha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.87,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You may call me Kuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.30,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't anyone's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.16,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Am I your husband, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.78,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not mind having your \Nchild or making you have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:54.82,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Have you got a Hanabatake \Nfarm in your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:56.13,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:59.81,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,The Crawling Chaos and Cthugha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:06.14,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Forks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:06.91,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.14,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.48,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Could this tsundere and \Nstabbing play come
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:14.35,Haiyore-internal/narrator,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that backstory \Nshe came up with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.50,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}from the bloodline of the cursed deity hunter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:16.69,Haiyore-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,was actually foreshadowing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.00,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}described in the black book?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:21.28,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Could his blood be flowing \Nin your veins, Mahiro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:22.88,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nyarko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:26.47,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh... I didn't think this \Nwould actually happen either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:27.44,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.54,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,get away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.29,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.79,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd encounter \Nthem in my own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:40.94,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to save your \Nson, not attack him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:44.30,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Hiro-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:45.90,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:48.55,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What? How could you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:53.93,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Shanta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.48,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! No, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.94,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,My, how cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:01.06,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,He seems harmless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:03.19,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell by looking at his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.06,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Shanta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:09.19,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you prefer my \Nmother-in-law to your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:11.08,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Is he your pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:13.80,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. As I have cute eyes as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:16.22,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not only harmless,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:19.71,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I have been protecting Mahiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.61,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting Hiro-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.09,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Could you explain that in detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:30.27,Haiyore-main,LUHI,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. It's finally \Ntime for all out war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:35.73,Haiyore-main,LUHI,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I will tear \Nthem out by the roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:43.23,Haiyore-ep-title,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Mothers Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:46.47,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,The Planetary Defense \NOrganization, aliens,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.74,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and Earth's entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.24,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I think I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:55.25,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Mother? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:58.15,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you holding him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:05:59.65,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.93,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm replenishing my sononium.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:04.25,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Sononium?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:06.38,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:09.26,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn to explain yourself, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:16.77,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I'm a deity hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:20.27,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What? A deity hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.36,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:33.16,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,My college seminar professor \Nwrote this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:42.67,book,BOOK,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(3900,1)}Deity Hunter Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:37.58,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Occasionally, that professor invites me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:41.74,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to help him hunt deities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:42.67,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.50,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Does Dad know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.39,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:49.06,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Married couples don't keep \Nsecrets from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:51.62,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a nice husband to allow me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:53.18,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to work a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:56.37,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I fell in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:00.19,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,The boy's parents are lovey dovey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:03.24,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be lovey dovey, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:04.79,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,In your case,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.44,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet there's a "craft" \Nhiding after the "love."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:11.45,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nyarko, let's be kissy \Nkissy lovey dovey together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:14.97,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pass on all sorts of\N weapons and defensive gear
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.95,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to the child we make.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:20.34,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Over my dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.35,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.02,Haiyore-overlap,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let go of me, Kuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:24.77,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't come back together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:26.49,Haiyore-overlap,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why don't you go mate \Nwith some nightgaunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:25.84,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:29.88,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he did everything he \Ncould to get days off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.99,Haiyore-overlap,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I will mate with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:31.94,Haiyore-overlap,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Enough already, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.42,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,To make up for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.84,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll probably be staying \Nat the office for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:35.83,Haiyore-overlap,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nyarko, when I am with \Nyou, the pain feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.62,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,The job might be called a "Deity Hunter"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.56,Haiyore-overlap,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're still breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.98,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not very dangerous work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.96,Haiyore-overlap,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kyubatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.60,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a part-time job. \NDon't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:42.60,Haiyore-overlap,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You were a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:46.11,Haiyore-internal/narrator,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:51.61,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Nyarko-san?\NI'm sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:54.52,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I jumped to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:58.60,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. That's not a problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:01.62,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You're such a \Ngood girl, Nyarko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:05.71,Haiyore-main,LUHI,0000,0000,0000,,Moving to secure target.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:08.91,Haiyore-main,LUHI,0000,0000,0000,,The hegemony of Earth is in our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:13.22,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Those filthy cheaters may \Nreturn at any moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.01,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so we must continue to defend him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:20.05,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Mom's back, \Nisn't your job over?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.17,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:23.71,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have the \Nimportant responsbility
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:25.90,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,of protecting Earth's Dreamlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:29.31,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I am hoping you will allow \Nus to continue using
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:31.78,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,this place as our base of operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:32.96,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:34.97,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.16,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mom? They can't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:40.77,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I wouldn't mind them staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:44.01,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:45.11,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot more \Nwrong with these two
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:46.74,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,than the look in their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:49.43,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't they protecting Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:53.05,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, \Nwouldn't we have to help them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:57.43,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you would understand, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:00.27,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I assume this means you've accepted me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:02.93,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,as a daughter-in-law of \Nthe Yasaka household.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:04.25,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:08.42,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Nyarko-san, you like Hiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:09.44,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:10.73,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.48,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seriously in love with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:16.11,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not sure I can
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:18.45,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,accept you as my daughter-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:21.95,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:27.54,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I want Hiro-kun to live \Na more normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.35,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm trying to say is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:31.55,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want the two of you to consider
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:35.47,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,your relationship more \Nseriously before committing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:36.97,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:40.08,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,But I {\i1}will{\i0} welcome you into my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:43.47,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll be Hiro-kun's \Nfriend forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:47.98,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Her SAN is quickly dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:51.86,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the gifts \Nyou've been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:55.92,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Tada! This time I got you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:59.10,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You bought another old \Nvideo game console.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:03.35,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say I'm \Nbuying my memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:07.87,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Paying for my fondest recollections.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:10.49,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. I want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:12.83,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You like games?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.38,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:16.74,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm sure we'll \Nhave a lot to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:18.57,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to play it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:22.35,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:26.37,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be you're hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:29.16,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:31.71,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.40,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.26,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat something \Nmade by you, Hiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:38.29,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I would like that also.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:39.39,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,So would I.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.11,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:48.04,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to add lots of sononium.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.42,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Add lots of vegetables, oil, and garlic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.60,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What should I make?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:10.17,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:11.60,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:15.57,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this would be \Nbetter if you had some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.28,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been said
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:21.53,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,a miracle occurs when you\N find your ultimate partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.62,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:27.91,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What loveless words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:31.79,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know what \Nyou'll try to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:36.17,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I know things have been that \Nway up until now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.67,mailign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,People (Deity)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:38.67,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,People learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:42.67,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you explain \Nwhat you have in your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:43.98,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,This thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:46.68,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,This brand of meat is \Nfamous even in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.47,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shub-Niggurath brand,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.81,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the Black Goat of the Woods \Nwith a Thousand Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:51.40,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.35,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I threw all of that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:57.10,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to make
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:12:00.82,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,something delicious for \Nyou and your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:04.87,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:05.92,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:08.61,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, but stick to Earth ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:09.58,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.56,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:13.31,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it my best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:15.58,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday anniversary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:18.24,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:22.31,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's discussing \Ngames with your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:26.68,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,They have game consoles in space?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:30.93,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,The X-oth and HS3 are the two favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:35.44,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Earth's game systems \Nare far more popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.00,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm going to use a sonic bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:44.99,Haiyore-eyecatch-an3,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,1)\an6}Haiyore! \NNyarko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:49.95,Haiyore-eyecatch-an1,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,1)}Haiyore! \NNyarko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:07.97,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:10.86,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you were a discerning \Nman, Mahiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:15.10,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you call \Na "yes/no cushion."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.86,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,"Bring it on, Mahiro-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.48,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,"Some people say hate when \Nthey really mean love."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:24.11,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's yes either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.23,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:30.62,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always prepared to accept you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.62,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nyarko goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:39.08,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's so soft and smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:38.25,Haiyore-overlap,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:40.05,Haiyore-overlap,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:43.27,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:45.44,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Morning sononium.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.26,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:52.26,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:55.27,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't behave \Nyourself, I'll hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.90,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hit people,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.40,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,unless you get to be a better boxer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.73,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:06.02,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Making you lose won't be so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:07.23,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:11.33,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you not to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:17.16,Haiyore-main,YORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.76,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.29,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.17,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:27.47,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Mahiro-san, I'll go on ahead and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.68,Haiyore-internal/narrator,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could return
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:38.79,Haiyore-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,to my normal life\N once my mom came home,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:42.52,Haiyore-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,but things have only gotten crazier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:50.97,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:55.20,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:15:00.80,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:02.57,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:08.72,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:11.82,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:16.47,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, are {\i1}you{\i0} hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:18.24,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.96,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even fall, \Nso don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.98,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:25.68,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:27.38,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't paying attention \Nto where I was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.95,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I was thinking \Nabout something, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:32.75,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:37.33,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's call it even.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.00,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:41.50,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.54,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.45,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:46.00,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:47.89,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.76,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,A nice guy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:56.06,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you repent?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:58.10,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,This is the path I chose myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.39,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:05.15,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Stop acting like idiots in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:11.28,Haiyore-main,YOICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:14.15,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm just tired this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:20.30,Haiyore-main,YOICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't know you had \Ntwo relatives your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:22.79,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:27.04,Haiyore-main,YOICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still have more relatives \Nyou don't know about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:30.05,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:34.55,Haiyore-main,TAMAO,0000,0000,0000,,Nyarko-chan, how have things \Nbeen with Yasaka-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:38.60,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't made any progress since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:42.27,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the shy Mahiro-san will ever
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:46.24,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,force me down and make a baby with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:50.06,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Tamao, do you have any \Nideas to drive Nyarko
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:51.57,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,crazy all night long?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:54.35,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Kuuko, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:56.57,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Tamao-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:59.45,Haiyore-main,TAMAO,0000,0000,0000,,An attack plan for your boyfriend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.58,Haiyore-main,TAMAO,0000,0000,0000,,How does this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:05.08,Haiyore-main,TAMAO,0000,0000,0000,,Emphasize your chest, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:08.59,Haiyore-main,TAMAO,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:11.72,Haiyore-main,YOICHI,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.97,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I just got chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:30.11,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Mahiro-san, how would you \Nlike a hot dog for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:34.62,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you tell me that \Nthing's proper name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:36.79,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Tindalos dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:39.53,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Go hit your head on a clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:40.47,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Eroba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:45.00,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I make good sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:48.38,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should ask.\NWhat kind of sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:50.91,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Dunwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:53.59,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to force \Nyourself to make jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.38,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Sad face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.63,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Mahiro-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:01.37,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,what is the sononium \Nyour mother mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:04.91,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem to be listed on \NEarth's periodic table of elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:06.85,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.73,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's something my mom made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:13.28,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,When she runs out, she says \Nher sadness maxes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:16.59,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Kuuko, what are you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:19.04,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,This month's Shonen Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:21.78,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What? Let me read that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:24.26,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Shonen Blood
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:27.29,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,was discontinued after issue 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:30.21,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,A space publisher picked it up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.67,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and started printing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:34.52,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,It happens all the time on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:37.02,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Games that would have \Nsold outside of Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:39.51,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,or consoles ahead of their time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.05,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:44.43,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,This magazine would have \Nsold outside of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:46.93,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:50.90,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Mahiro-san. Mahiro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.94,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,The boy left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:55.48,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What? Without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.51,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,So I waited for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:58.83,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:11.79,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're that kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.59,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,You're the guy from this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:17.70,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.62,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:24.14,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.85,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.35,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:33.31,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You're looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:36.62,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I can't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:43.37,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:46.98,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never been in a \Nstore like this before,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:48.44,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was sort of scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.37,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:54.00,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I made you come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:57.32,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I was hungry anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:00.00,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:04.07,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,We must be bound by the \Nred string of fate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.64,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to meet in a place like this, Mahiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:09.64,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What, did you follow me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:13.08,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a nice thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:17.28,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,The center of ultimate \Nchaos told me to buy more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:18.27,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,More.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:21.23,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:23.16,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Nyarko-chan and Kuuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:25.96,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Hasuta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:28.03,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:30.93,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean this kid's an alien, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:32.21,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:36.71,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hastur, the great deity of wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:37.81,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:40.42,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You said "-kun"... he's a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.54,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes to that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:47.74,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,We have known Hasuta-kun \Nsince space kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:49.40,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,In space elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:51.93,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasuta-kun was our student \Ncouncil president.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:55.19,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just add \N"space" to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:57.99,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you two \Nwere civil servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:20:59.99,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,The job security must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:01.57,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I am a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:03.97,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,If a shut-in like you \Ncan use her connections
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:06.70,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to become a civil servant,\N you must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:09.93,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hasuta-kun, what are you doing on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:11.60,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:14.59,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you mention in one \Nof your New Year's cards
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.59,0:21:17.76,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd become a librarian \Nat the Celaeno Library?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:20.05,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What a stereotypical card.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:22.74,Haiyore-main,NASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, my father asked me to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:24.05,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,help him with his work,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:26.22,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I quit my job at the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.73,0:21:30.20,Haiyore-main,KUUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hasuta-kun, what does your father do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:33.23,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:36.39,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were looking \Nfor someone earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:37.97,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you're helping him with?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:42.20,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They live somewhere around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:44.09,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not good with directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:45.22,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What's the address?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:47.92,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,I only know the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:52.24,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,It's someone called Yasaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:57.46,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What's the name of the \Nperson you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:04.19,Haiyore-main,HASUTA,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yasaka Yoriko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.26,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:09.33,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:43.16,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting down\Nto our wedding, Mahiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.16,0:23:44.39,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.39,0:23:45.71,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,These cute little lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:47.53,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You made a terrible first impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.53,0:23:50.40,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally putting into motion \Nmy plan to overcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:53.33,Haiyore-main,NYARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode is \N"Let's Go Great Conspiracy X!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.33,0:23:54.77,Haiyore-main,MAHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.77,0:23:56.77,Haiyore-main,,0000,0000,0000,,
